lead_paragraph: The seventh inning took 72 minutes to complete, saw 21 batters come up, and twelve runs cross the plate. It gave the Los Angeles Dodgers' offense the opportunity for its most memorable outburst yet.

headline.print_headline: Grandal's Single Caps 5-Run Rally as Dodgers Beat D-Backs
